{
  "stem": "3848.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And anti-Semitism was part of that part of Rowne because Rowne before the first World War belonged to Russia and all the pogroms that happened during the Russian-- the Russian, that Czar that was there before the revolution.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So sort of, the Jews accepted it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's why we always wanted to have our children sort of go to Israel and build their own country.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we had to live with the situation like that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "During holidays, like Christmas and New Year's, most of the Jews would be sitting in the houses, not go out because after the-- the-- the masses, church, people would come out.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They would so worked out that they would be hitting or beating up the Jews for something that happened 2,000 years ago.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My-- my-- well, sort of observant.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were celebrating Shabbos, which is Saturday.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My father used to come home because he always used to work in Obariv.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's a little town out of the city.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was a tailor among the Ukrainian people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was a little town that just Ukrainian people lived there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they liked us very much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We-- I used to go there and play with the Ukrainian people, speak to them in their language.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were sort of friends.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In the city of Rowne, it was a little different.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There, you mixed among your own Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I was very happy to be in that little town, Obariv.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we had friends.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "My father had friends.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And therefore, for Saturday, he used to come home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So he was away all week.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And Saturday or Friday night, he used to come home and leave on Sunday again for the week to work.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
